Detailed Description

cvmx_npi_pci_int_arb_cfg

NPI_PCI_INT_ARB_CFG = Configuration For PCI Arbiter

Controls operation of the Internal PCI Arbiter. This register should only be written when PRST# is asserted. NPI_PCI_INT_ARB_CFG[EN] should only be set when Octane is a host.
